y Reed]] \u2013 production\n* Jordan Reynolds \u2013 production\n* [[Romans (musician)|Romans]] \u2013 production\n* Rush Hr \u2013 production\n* Matthew Tavares \u2013 production\n* The Monsters and the Strangerz \u2013 production\n* Westen Weiss \u2013 production\n* [[Jon Bellion]] \u2013 miscellaneous production\n* Cashmere Cat \u2013 [[Record producer|additional production]]\n* Bart Schoudel \u2013 vocal production\n* Gregg Golterman \u2013 production coordination\n* Christian Johnson \u2013 production coordination\n* Jeremy \"J Boogs\" Levin \u2013 production coordination\n* David Silberstein \u2013 production coordination\n{{div col end}}\n\n=== Technical ===\n{{div col}}\n* [[Mike Bozzi]] \u2013 [[Mastering (audio)|mastering]]\n* Dave Kutch \u2013 mastering\n*Chris Galland \u2013 [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|mixing]], [[Audio engineer|assistant engineering]]\n*Serben Ghenea \u2013 mixing\n*John Hanes \u2013 mixing, [[Audio engineer|engineering]]\n*[[Manny Marroquin]] \u2013 mixing\n*Benny Blanco \u2013 [[Program music|programming]]\n*Cashmere Cat \u2013 programming\n*DJ Hardwerk \u2013 programming\n*German \u2013 programming\n*Mattman & Robin \u2013 programming\n*The Monsters and the Strangerz \u2013 programming\n*Watt \u2013 programming\n*Nick Taylor \u2013 engineering\n*Nathaniel Alford \u2013 [[Audio engineer|recording]], [[Audio engineer|vocal engineering]]\n*Louis Bell \u2013 recording, vocal engineering\n*Ryan Dulude \u2013 recording\n*Paul Lamalfa \u2013 recording\n*Dustin Park \u2013 recording\n*Jordan Reynolds \u2013 recording\n*Bart Schoudel \u2013 recording, vocal engineering\n*Brian Taylor \u2013 recording\n*Zubin Thakkar \u2013 vocal engineering\n{{div col end}}\n\n=== Business and design ===\n{{div col}}\n* Anita Marisa Boriboon \u2013 creative direction\n* Amber Park \u2013 creative direction, design\n* Diego L. Rodriguez \u2013 design assistant\n* Bella P. Santos \u2013 design assistant\n* Alana Truong \u2013 design assistant\n* Amanda Charchian \u2013 photography\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019\u20132020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Argentine Albums ([[Argentine Chamber of Phonograms and Videograms Producers|CAPIF]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.diariodecultura.com.ar/rankings/los-discos-mas-vendidos-de-la-semana-3/|title=Los discos m\u00e1s vendidos de la semana|work=Diario de Cultura|publisher=[[Argentine Chamber of Phonograms and Videograms Producers|CAPIF]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217140300/https://www.diariodecultura.com.ar/rankings/los-discos-mas-vendidos-de-la-semana-3/|archivedate=December 17, 2019|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n{{album chart|Australia|6|artist=Camila Cabello|album=Romance|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Austria|35|artist=Camila Cabello|album=Romance|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 19, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Flanders|16|artist=Camila Cabello|album=Romance|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Wallonia|58|artist=Camila Cabello|album=Romance|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|BillboardCanada|1|artist=Camila Cabello|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 17, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Denmark|32|M|url=http://hitlisten.nu/default.asp?w=1&y=2020&list=a40|title=Hitlisten.NU \u2013 Album Top-40 Uge 52, 2019|publisher=[[Hitlisten]]|artist=Camila Cabello|album=Romance|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 8, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Netherlands|8|artist=Camila Cabello|album=Romance|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 13, 2019}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Estonian Albums (''[[Eesti Ekspress]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ekspress.delfi.ee/areen/eesti-tipp-40-muusikas-aasta-algas-uute-tabeliliidritega?id=88590583|title=ALBUMID TIPP-40|work=[[Eesti Ekspress]]|date=January 10, 2020|acces