ed.com/video/Muqeem-Khan-Playful-technology|title=TED2013 Talent Search|accessdate=December 14, 2015}}</ref><ref name=BrightFuture>{{cite web|url=http://www.muqeemkhan.com/BrightFuture.html|title=Untitled Document|accessdate=December 14, 2015}}</ref><ref name=Blending>[http://www.muqeemkhan.com/press/Qatar_Tribune_Nation_page_23.pdf'' \u2022 \u201cBlending Real With Virtual\u201d, Qatar Tribune, Doha, Qatar, May, 2009.'']</ref><ref name=Digital>[http://www.thenews.com.pk/TodaysPrintDetail.aspx?ID=159280&Cat=4&dt=1/24/2009'' \u2022 \u201cDigital age in Pakistan not a distant dream\u201d, The News, Karachi, Pakistan, January, 2011.'']</ref><ref name=Final-Fantasy>[https://movies.nytimes.com/movie/246683/Final-Fantasy-the-Spirits-Within/credits'' \u2022 Final-Fantasy-the-Spirits-Within - Cast, Crew, Director and Awards - NYTimes.com. (n.d.). Retrieved September 11, 2013, from http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/246683/Final-Fantasy-the-Spirits-Within/credits'']</ref><ref name=Total>[http://www.muqeemkhan.com/press/Total%20Realism%20Penunsula%202013.pdf ''\u2022 \u201cTotal realism with computer graphics no distant dream\u201d, Qatar Tribune, Doha, Qatar, March, 2013.'', February 25, 2013]</ref><ref name=anim2>{{cite web|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/110559/animation-in-pakistani-feature-films/|title=Animation in Pakistani feature films|date=January 28, 2011|work=The Express Tribune|accessdate=December 14, 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Nadia Ali (singer)|Nadia Ali]] \u2013 [[Grammy]]-nominated singer-songwriter and former frontwoman of [[iiO (dance group)|iiO]]; known for the song \"[[Rapture (iiO song)|Rapture]]\"; one of the prominent vocalists of [[electronic dance music]]; has collaborated with DJs [[Armin van Buuren]], [[John Creamer & Stephane K]] and [[BT (musician)|BT]]\n* [[Nadia Ali (actress)|Nadia Ali]] \u2013 erotic dancer and former actress in pornographic films \n*[[Nargis Fakhri]] \u2013 actress and model of half Pakistani and half Czech descent\n*[[Naureen Zaim]] \u201