d for 2015.<ref>{{cite news|first=Demelza |last=De Burca |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/TV3+ringing+the+changes+as+Midweek+gets+the+axe.-a0375207225 |title=TV3 ringing the changes as Midweek gets the axe |publisher=Trinity Mirror |newspaper=Irish Mirror |date=17 July 2014 |accessdate=16 February 2015}}</ref>\n*17 July \u2013 [[TG4]] begins broadcasting its content in the United States via the Today's Ireland channel.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2014/0717/631400-tg4-launches-nationwide-broadcasting-in-the-usa/ |title=TG4 launches nationwide broadcasting in the USA |work=RT\u00c9 Ten |publisher=RT\u00c9 |date=17 July 2014 |accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref>\n*23 July \u2013 TG4 announce the appointment of three new weather presenters\u2014Irial \u00d3 Ceallaigh, Fiona N\u00ed Fhlaithearta and Caitl\u00edn Nic Aoidh\u2014who were selected following a public competition.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2014/0723/632577-tg4-introduces-three-new-weather-presenters/ |title=TG4 introduces three new weather presenters |work=RT\u00c9 Ten |publisher=RT\u00c9 |date=23 July 2014 |accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref>\n*31 July \u2013 ''[[The Herald (Ireland)|The Evening Herald]]'' reports that RT\u00c9 has commissioned a documentary about pornography to be aired as part of its autumn schedule.<ref>{{cite news|last=Finn |first=Melanie |url=http://www.herald.ie/entertainment/porno-documentary-for-rte-schedule-30474369.html |title=Porno documentary for RT\u00c9 schedule |publisher=Independent News and Media |newspaper=The Evening Herald |date=31 July 2014 |accessdate=6 April 2015}}</ref> The two-part documentary, ''We Need to Talk About Porn'', airs on RT\u00c9 One in January 2015.<ref name=\"RT\u00c9 Ten\">{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2015/0105/669341-rte-tens-tv-picks-for-today-monday-january-5/ |title=RT\u00c9 TEN'S TV picks for today Monday January 5 |work=RT\u00c9 Ten |publisher=RT\u00c9 |date=5 January 2015 |accessdate=27 June 2015