ews/politics/former-journalist-and-politician-ted-nealon-dies-aged-84-1.1671120 |title=Former journalist and politician Ted Nealon dies aged 84 |newspaper=The Irish Times |publisher=The Irish Times Trust |date=28 January 2014 |accessdate=29 March 2014}}</ref>\n* 11 February \u2013 [[Ronnie Masterson]], 87; actress.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishexaminer.com/breakingnews/entertainment/rest-in-peace-mam-miss-you-aonghus-tweets-tribute-to-mother-ronnie-622355.html |title='Rest in peace mam. Miss you': Aonghus tweets tribute to mother Ronnie |publisher= |work=Irish Examiner |date=11 February 2014 |accessdate=29 March 2014}}</ref>\n* 10 March \u2013 [[Eileen Colgan]], 80; actress.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/tv-radio/fair-city-and-glenroe-actress-eileen-colgan-dies-30079946.html |title=Fair City and Glenroe actress Eileen Colgan dies |publisher=Independent News and Media |newspaper=The Irish Independent |date=10 March 2014 |accessdate=29 March 2014}}</ref>\n*21 March \u2013 Oliver Maloney, 77, former [[Director-General of RT\u00c9]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/about/en/press-office/press-releases/2014/0321/603801-oliver-maloney-former-director-general-rte/ |title=Oliver Maloney, former Director-General, RT\u00c9 |publisher=RT\u00c9 |work=RT\u00c9 News |date=21 March 2014 |accessdate=11 February 2015}}</ref>\n*22 July \u2013 [[Louis Lentin]], 80: theatre, film and television director<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/news/2014/0723/632599-louis-lenton/ |title='Dear Daughter' director Louis Lentin dies |publisher=RT\u00c9 |work=RT\u00c9 News |date=23 July 2014 |accessdate=11 February 2015}}</ref>\n*10 August \u2013 [[Ann Rowan]], 85, actress (''[[The Riordans]]'', ''[[Father Ted]]'').<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2014/0811/636368-the-riordans-actress-ann-rowan-has-died/ |title=The Riordans actress Ann Rowan has died |publisher=RT\u00c9 |work=RT\u00c9 News |date=11 August 2014 |accessdate=11 February 2015