.ie/entertainment/tv-radio/i-need-a-new-challenge-says-sybil-mulcahy-as-she-takes-tv3-redundancy-after-16-years-30963058.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=4 February 2015 |title=\u2018I need a new challenge,\u2019 says Sybil Mulcahy as she takes TV3 redundancy after 16 years |publisher=Independent News and Media |newspaper=The Evening Herald |date=4 February 2015 |accessdate=4 February 2015 }}</ref>\n*5 February \u2013 RT\u00c92 confirms it will air ''[[Eurovision Song Contest's Greatest Hits|Eurovision's Greatest Hits]]'', a concert celebrating 60 years of the [[Eurovision Song Contest]], which will be shown throughout Europe over the Easter weekend.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2015/0205/677984-rte2-to-air-eurovisions-greatest-hits/ |title=RT\u00c92 to air Eurovision's Greatest Hits |work=RT\u00c9 Ten |publisher=RT\u00c9 |date=5 February 2015 |accessdate=8 April 2015}}</ref>\n*9 February \u2013 [[Setanta Sports]] announces that it has gained exclusive live broadcasting rights to [[UEFA Champions League|Champions League]] and [[Europa League]] football for three years from 2015\u201316. However, RT\u00c9 has retained the television and online rights to show Wednesday Champions League matches, while TV3 will show Tuesday Champions League matches.<ref>{{cite news|first=Brynmor |last=Pattison |url=http://www.irishmirror.ie/sport/soccer/soccer-news/setanta-sports-gains-television-rights-5133120 |title=Setanta Sports gains television rights for Champions League and exclusive rights for Europa League |publisher=Trinity Mirror |newspaper=The Irish Mirror |date=9 February 2015 |accessdate=14 February 2015}}</ref>\n*9 February \u2013 A man who appears in the TV3 documentary series ''Prison Families'' is given a suspended sentence at Dublin's Circuit Criminal Court after his trial was told that a robbery and an attempted robbery he committed took place at the time of other offences, and should have been considered at a previous trial.<ref>{{cite news|firs