oline Morahan takes time out of Hollywood to sign up for TG4 |publisher=Independent News and Media |newspaper=The Evening Herald |date=28 April 2015 |accessdate=30 April 2015}}</ref>\n*30 April \u2013 It is reported that businessman [[Denis O'Brien]] is seeking an injunction to stop RT\u00c9 airing a story about his private banking details. The case will be heard before the [[High Court (Ireland)|High Court]] on 1 May.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thejournal.ie/denis-obrien-rte-injunction-2078594-Apr2015/ |title=Denis O\u2019Brien wants an injunction to stop RT\u00c9 airing a story about him |publisher=Distilled Media |work=Thejournal.ie |date=30 April 2015 |accessdate=30 April 2015}}</ref>\n*30 April \u2013 RT\u00c9 announce that [[Henry Shefflin]] has signed up as a pundit on RT\u00c92's ''[[The Sunday Game]]''.<ref>{{cite news|first=John |last=Fogarty |url=http://www.irishexaminer.com/breakingnews/sport/shefflin-chooses-rte-over-sky-sports-675168.html |title=Shefflin chooses RT\u00c9 over Sky Sports |publisher=Landmark Media Investments |newspaper=The Irish Examiner |date=30 April 2015 |accessdate=30 April 2015}}</ref>\n\n===May===\n*1 May \u2013 The High Court places a temporary injunction on the broadcast of an RT\u00c9 story about businessman Denis O'Brien until 12 May, while a full hearing on the issue takes place.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thejournal.ie/rte-denis-obrien-2079413-May2015/ |title=An RT\u00c9 story about Denis O\u2019Brien has been blocked until at least 12 May |publisher=Distilled Media |work=Thejournal.ie |date=1 May 2015 |accessdate=1 May 2015}}</ref>\n*1 May \u2013 After agreeing a deal with Endemol, TV3 announce they will broadcast ''[[Big Brother (UK)|Big Brother UK]]'', the [[Big Brother 16 (UK)|sixteenth series]] of which begins airing on TV3 and [[3e]] from 12 May.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.tv3.ie/xpose/article/entertainment-news/165818/TV3-brings-Big-Brother-back-to-Irish-screens |title=TV3 brings Big Brother back to Irish 